{"type": "article", "id": 16744, "title": "大胆地使用木材之后，一家老餐馆就完全变了样子", "description": "亚速尔群岛是一个火山喷发形成的岛屿。上面有个迷人的餐馆。", "date": "2015-10-29T18:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3253, "name": "葡萄牙"}, {"id": 4814, "name": "餐厅设计"}, {"id": 17950, "name": "FCC建筑事务所"}, {"id": 17951, "name": "Paulo Lobo"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 244, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607125659c7im5YnlvrEPBLU2.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t餐厅扩建是不少建筑事务所面临的课题，这家位于葡萄牙亚速尔群岛（ Azores ）中的皮库(Pico)岛上带酒吧的餐厅，原本只有一个火山岩墙面的老房子，来自葡萄牙的 FCC 建筑事务所的设计师直接在外面加了一个木……桶。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这个木质装置的外形有些像酒桶或者鲸鱼，它充当了餐厅新的入口，二楼直接与后面房子的二楼相连。它有着圆形的门，圆孔或长条的窗，在外形、材质和颜色上都与后面的老房子产生强烈的对比，非常醒目。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125648CX4JVbtc9rOu83sn.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125648QhPvn7ExGYfKrNO4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125649fK8mMHCEodvhkxFL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125650D7OZLv3wixEIkUa1.jpg\" title=\"鸟瞰图\" alt=\"鸟瞰图\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>鸟瞰图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t室内设计来自 Paulo Lobo，也使用了松木装饰墙面、屋顶和家具，配上圆筒形状的空间，有些像一个船舱。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261440179qArJBCt3iTLoFWY.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144018D3bPZuqr9hvsTUIG.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071256507dFRfXD0EriPJB8o.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"1.04278729\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144019hrEV5iopkuQXZLRH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"772\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144020L5ESQganlNBZhK7G.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125651Hu8clPWkwsiNASG3.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071256511sSyDvndFjuRzVB6.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125652qxwkvYEf7DltMpzF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125652fKtux0J8B9eIGHdT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.07334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125653gU9fo1Ou86KTX0lI.jpg\" title=\"石砌房子的室内也做了刷新\" alt=\"石砌房子的室内也做了刷新\" data-ratio=\"1.06601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">原来的<span>石砌房子室内也做了刷新</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t按照设计师的话说，它结合了岛屿、岩石、鲸鱼、酒桶等与周围环境相关的元素，创造出一个自由开放的空间。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这家餐厅从夏天就开始营业，可以去喝下午茶以及举办周末音乐会。楼上也增加了一些桌椅，可以看到大西洋的夜晚，天黑下来，这里显得宁静而温柔。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125653qpvPi2rf6UYangCh.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125654IQdCMgK9TZGn7Jre.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071256548P1WD0iBlyAQvEH4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125655tViOwXNjZv86ucS4.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125655US78mNknfHOKp6YR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125655BQKUGdgY6vbZLqV2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125656HRSokhgcIVYz0uwt.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从二楼平台看大西洋\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144021SzvM7Ue1DfuAKNYW.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071256573Wjk71IcmE48XuYD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125657qteSDEd4fYylQLoI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125658syFKhdl7X2e4LZGO.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.752\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125658LUjq9urRYz2GbaPw.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.062\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125659JRbZKOAnW8hN1jo7.gif\" title=\"平面图\" alt=\"平面图\" data-ratio=\"0.403\" data-format=\"gif\"><span>侧面图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>图片来自<a href=\"http://www.dezeen.com/2015/10/27/cella-bar-by-fcc-arquitectura-volcanic-stone-barn-whale-inspired-extension-restaurants-bar/\" target=\"_blank\"> dezeen</a>、<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/architecture/fcc-arquitectura-paulo-lobo-cella-bar-pico-island-azores-portugal-10-27-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom</a></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}